    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors against the MRL 5 requirements documented in the project requirements specification. Seven factors were assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Despite these deficiencies, the sponsor has accepted the package under the Minimal profile binding, acknowledging that the structured bindsRequirement linkage is not populated and that the assessment is accepted with the understanding that full compliance with project requirements will be demonstrated in a subsequent revision. The decision reflects the sponsor's risk tolerance for the current design phase rather than a finding of full credibility.",
